title: Jack Kerouac, New York
inscriptions: Signed in lower margin: Jack Kerouac passing statue of Samuel Cox, Tomkins Square Park Lower East Side Manhattan, walking west up East 7th Street from my apartment toward corner of Avenue A and Leshko's Ukranian Restaurant-he's making a Dostosevsky madface Russian basso Bebop"om!"-we were just wandering around the subterranean neighborhood, Fall 1953.  Allen Ginsberg
